`contextIsolation: true` · `nodeIntegration: false` · **`sandbox: false`** — do not flip without testing

## Voice IPC (`main.js`)

| Handle | Notes |
|--------|-------|
| `voice:status` | TTS + STT readiness |
| `voice:system-prompt` | Claude system prompt |
| `voice:vad-port` | VAD WebSocket URL |
| `voice:warm-tts` | warm TTS + STT stack |
| `voice:transcribe` | audio → text via STT router |
| `voice:ask-claude` | Claude completion |
| `voice:speak` | TTS synthesis |
| `voice:assistant-turn` | Claude + streaming TTS |
| `voice:set-voice` / `voice:get-voice` | TTS voice selection |
| `voice:start-wake-word-listening` | begin wake-word detection |
| `voice:stop-wake-word-listening` | end wake-word detection |
| `voice:detect-wake-word` | check audio for "hey Retron" |
| `voice:detect-stop-command` | check text for "go to sleep" |

Events: `voice:tts-chunk` · `voice:claude-delta` — Warm: `voice:warm-tts` only

